{"meta": {"centerNodeId": "taxonomy-species-brachygalba-goeringi", "centerNodeType": "taxonomy", "generatedAt": "2026-05-28T16:28:22", "includedNodeCount": 3, "includedLinkCount": 2, "layoutMode": "precomputed-static"}, "center": {"id": "taxonomy-species-brachygalba-goeringi", "name": "Pale-headed jacamar", "type": "taxonomy"}, "nodes": [{"id": "bird-pale-headed-jacamar-d6aa5c7c", "name": "Pale-headed jacamar", "englishName": "Pale-headed jacamar", "latinName": "Brachygalba goeringi", "type": "bird", "status": "LC", "summary": "The pale-headed jacamar (Brachygalba goeringi) is a species of bird in the family Galbulidae. It is found in Colombia and Venezuela. Taxonomy and systematics The pale-headed jacamar is monotypic. It and the dusky-backed (B. salmoni), brown (B. lugubris), and white-throated jacamars (B. albogularis) form a superspecies. Description The pale-headed jacamar is 16.5 to 18 cm (6.5 to 7.1 in) long and weighs 16 to 18 g (0.56 to 0.63 oz). The male's crown, nape, and shoulders are ashy brown. The rest of the upper parts are dark brown glossed with greenish; they look blue-black when worn. It has a pale supercilium and a buffy-white throat. It has a chestnut band on the upper belly and dark brown flanks; the rest of the underparts are white. The female is almost identical. The juvenile has a gray crown and nape, and the upper parts are brighter and the green gloss stronger. Distribution and habitat The pale-headed jacamar is found from Arauca and Casanare Departments in Colombia north through northwestern Venezuela at least to Lara. It primarily inhabits the edges of gallery and secondary forest in llanos grasslands. In elevation it ranges as high as 1,100 m (3,600 ft) but is usually found much lower. Behavior Feeding The pale-headed jacamar's diet is insects, mostly Lepidoptera and Odonata. It often perches on emergent branches in pairs or small family groups and sallies from there to catch its flying prey. Breeding The pale-headed jacamar nests in burrows in earth banks. Nesting has been noted in Venezuela during April and May. Vocalization The pale-headed jacamar's song is a series of high \"weet\" notes that increase in speed and pitch and ends with a trill [1]. Status The IUCN has assessed the pale-headed jacamar as being of Least Concern. It is \"[c]ommon throughout its range...\" and \"[n]o specific threats [are] documented so far, despite overall habitat loss in certain areas as a result of deforestation. References External links Pale-headed jacamar videos on the Internet Bird Collection Pale-headed jacamar photo gallery Archived 2011-05-16 at the Wayback Machine VIREO Photo-Medium Res Archived 2008-02-26 at the Wayback Machine Photo Archived 2016-03-03 at the Wayback Machine; Article home.scarlet.be Picture; Article classicnatureprints", "shortSummary": "The pale-headed jacamar (Brachygalba goeringi) is a species of bird in the family Galbulidae. It is found in Colombia and Venezuela.", "locations": ["哥伦比亚", "委內瑞拉", "Gallery forest", "次生林", "亞諾斯"], "habitats": ["稀树草原"], "threats": ["栖息地破坏", "森林砍伐"], "lat": 4.0, "lng": -72.0, "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Brachygalba_goeringi_-_Ben_Costamagna_-_465063478.jpeg/960px-Brachygalba_goeringi_-_Ben_Costamagna_-_465063478.jpeg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-brachygalba", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-brachygalba-goeringi", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-brachygalba", "species": "taxonomy-species-brachygalba-goeringi"}, "expandable": true, "x": -123.95, "y": -249.08, "z": 579.08}, {"id": "taxonomy-genus-brachygalba", "name": "Brachygalba", "latinName": "Brachygalba", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "genus", "summary": "Brachygalba（Brachygalba）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联4种鸟类，如White-throated jacamar、Brown jacamar、Pale-headed jacamar等4种鸟类。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 4, "x": 79.18, "y": 654.76, "z": -79.27}, {"id": "taxonomy-species-brachygalba-goeringi", "name": "Pale-headed jacamar", "latinName": "Brachygalba goeringi", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "species", "summary": "Pale-headed jacamar（Brachygalba goeringi）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联1种鸟类，如Pale-headed jacamar。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 1, "x": -123.95, "y": -249.08, "z": 590.03}], "links": [{"key": "bird-pale-headed-jacamar-d6aa5c7c__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-brachygalba-goeringi", "source": "bird-pale-headed-jacamar-d6aa5c7c", "target": "taxonomy-species-brachygalba-goeringi", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属于种", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 中的种字段补充。"}, {"key": "taxonomy-species-brachygalba-goeringi__belongs_to_genus__taxonomy-genus-brachygalba", "source": "taxonomy-species-brachygalba-goeringi", "target": "taxonomy-genus-brachygalba", "relation": "belongs_to_genus", "label": "属于属", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 分类字段补充：Pale-headed jacamar 属于属 Brachygalba。"}]}
